#Data preprocessing of Value, Wage, Height and Weight

#currency
def convert_currency(x):
    x = x.replace('â¬','')
    if x.endswith("M"):
        return float(x.split("M")[0]) * 1000000
    elif x.endswith("K"):
        return float(x.split("K")[0]) * 1000
fifa['Value'] = fifa['Value'].apply(convert_currency)
fifa['Wage'] = fifa['Wage'].apply(convert_currency)

#Height (inches)
def feet_to_inches(x):
    tmp = x.split("'")
    return int(tmp[0]) * 12 + int(tmp[1])
fifa["Height"] = fifa["Height"].apply(feet_to_inches)

#Weight
fifa["Weight"] = fifa["Weight"].str.replace("lbs", "")
fifa["Weight"] = fifa["Weight"].astype('float')

#The cups
gold = worldcups['Winner']
silver = worldcups['Runners-Up']
bronze = worldcups['Third']

gold_count = pd.DataFrame.from_dict(gold.value_counts())
silver_count = pd.DataFrame.from_dict(silver.value_counts())
bronze_count = pd.DataFrame.from_dict(bronze.value_counts())

Total = pd.concat([gold_count,silver_count,bronze_count], axis=1)
Total = Total.fillna(0)
Total.reset_index()
Total.rename(index = {"Czechoslovakia":"Czech Republic","USA":"United States"}, inplace = True)
Total = Total.sort_values(by= ["Winner","Runners-Up","Third"], ascending = False)

Total.ix[:,:].plot(kind='bar',y=["Winner","Runners-Up","Third"], color=['gold','silver','brown'], width = 0.8, 
                   figsize = (10,4))
plt.xlabel('Countries')
plt.xticks(rotation = 60)
plt.ylabel('Times')
plt.show()

def defending(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Marking', 'StandingTackle', 
                               'SlidingTackle']].sum())))

def general(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['HeadingAccuracy', 'Dribbling', 'Curve', 
                               'BallControl']].sum())))

def mental(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Aggression', 'Interceptions', 'Positioning', 
                               'Vision','Composure']].sum())))

def passing(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Crossing', 'ShortPassing', 
                               'LongPassing']].sum())))

def mobility(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Acceleration', 'SprintSpeed', 
                               'Agility','Reactions']].sum())))
def power(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Balance', 'Jumping', 'Stamina', 
                               'Strength']].sum())))

def rating(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Potential', 'Overall']].sum())))

def shooting(fifatop20):
    return int(round((fifatop20[['Finishing', 'Volleys', 'FKAccuracy', 
                               'ShotPower','LongShots', 'Penalties']].sum())))
